{"tid":1287554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登公投】烈士自殺　應該大肆報道　定係冷處理？","createTime":"2019-07-05T09:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:23:07.000Z","uid":14328,"like":6,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2075e3c688f7a0f516f34e4059b251ffc12730e4","tid":1287554,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"截至７月５日<br />\n<br />\n以身殉道嘅烈士，有四名，但現時嘅新聞報導明顯不足，有烈士自殺後，其姓名更從未被報導。大眾間，無留意網路新聞／消息者，更從來未聽過有示威者自殺。<br />\n<br />\n烈士殺身成仁，志在以身軀喚起更多人關注事件，令香港人抗爭意志更為堅定，故此，有人認為應大肆報道。<br />\n<br />\n但有人認為烈士自殺應冷處理，以防有他人效法，令負面情緒蔓延。更不應冠以烈士之名，鼓吹自殺之風。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔，你地認為烈士自殺，應該大肆報道，定係冷處理？<br />\n<br />\n大肆報道 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冷處理 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：個人認為熱心參與今次運動既人，一定會知道已經有４個人自殺，情已殤，心已累。由衷希望唔好再有第五個。但係，冷處理左去，豈非漠視烈士以死喚醒他人之意？現今四名殉道者，均有話想說，有道所求，唔係應該將佢地既心意傳出去？傳比每一個香港人知，傳比全世界知，喺呢個21世紀嘅文明世界，身為「自由港」嘅國際都市&mdash;香港有四名烈士，因中國暴政而亡？<br />\n<br />\n好想知道咁多位連登仔點睇"},{"pid":"b02b3677727ba68ecdff4f0be9b65af890833ea7","tid":1287554,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},{"pid":"641b8974c78e6fc26e04a49d1770ada2506aeb5e","tid":1287554,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"如果係想以死明志，就應留番條命，勇武歡迎你嘅加入<br />\n如果係因為心灰，就更加唔應該再大幅報導自殺新聞，令手足更心灰，掀起自殺潮"},{"pid":"3aabfb4ae2a8528f0106c7636e42803e91be96cf","tid":1287554,"uid":47256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060709/6110027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060709%2F6110027&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=faa8f3e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060709%2F6110027&h=4f6eb292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060709/6110027</a><br />\n<br />\n自殺是會傳染的<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4bb5951645a8ff0602f3e10767eac85ae109ef","tid":1287554,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:16:27.000Z","msg":"以死明志呢個行為根本就唔值得鼓勵<br />\n政府根本就唔會理你<br />\n反而令到自己人傷心<br />\n而且英雄化只會令更多人效法<br />\n更多人擔心<br />\n自己人本身力量都唔多<br />\n所以請愛惜生命<br />\n用黎做更有意義既事<br />\n我地需要你<br />\n但唔需要你既生命"},{"pid":"da201e46c34ea23d0af3de1a5649a9e5eb9b0512","tid":1287554,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:16:53.000Z","msg":"冷咩撚野處理呀用埋d大陸字"},{"pid":"2dc58bd98ae64ac6f7d67702a37a498d61ee5725","tid":1287554,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rhjMbT4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrhjMbT4.png&h=53408b2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"221819cedd66d4b28495133af4b15e94aefd07bf","tid":1287554,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da201e46c34ea23d0af3de1a5649a9e5eb9b0512","tid":1287554,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:16:53.000Z","msg":"冷咩撚野處理呀用埋d大陸字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"Sorrry 文化水平唔夠高，唔知冷處理係大陸字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n修正用返「大事化小」"},{"pid":"ded2702b2871887dab6329ad58f8ea48b21c0503","tid":1287554,"uid":28728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"自殺係滅己方士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冷血d講<br />\n如果已置生死於度外<br />\n不如下次去成為前線/支援前線<br />\n唔怕死嘅你地其實好珍貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跳一個我地嘅戰士就少一個"}]}